{"id":402585,"date":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":21}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"154","ytitle":"","mtitle":"风钻手","ftitle":"","authors":["朔风"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朔风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拴紧绳索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬挂高空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风钻手象一只山鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘旋在云中!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云烟缭绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈深渊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山风刮得越狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你手中的风钻吼得越响；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪纷飞中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你叫崖壁飞出万点火花!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁猜不透你的心?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你恨不得一眨眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打好一排埋药孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天内就把大山凿通!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁猜不透你的心?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要叫轰隆轰隆的火车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立刻穿过千山万岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让内地和边疆连通!"}]}